body:
### Welcome to something incomplete.
This section will be a brief but eye catching intro that highlights my specialties (if I had any)

```
$ this was in the template
$ showing some random git commands
$ the markdown was pretty cool so I'll just keep it like this
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac I won't be able to help you because I've only used Github for Linux and Windows

### Designer Templates
I've chosen a template provided by Github using a Random Number Generator I coded in Visual Basic 6 back in 2009 because I'm too lazy to redo it in VB.net

### Will this eventually not suck
At some point, hopefully before anyone important sees this page I'll rewrite this page with actual relevant information about me and a UI that is more involved than me clicking a button.

### Authors and Contributors
I would like to thank GitHub for writing 100% of the styling for page and myself for providing 95% of the text.

### Support or Contact
This site doesn't do anything and therefore I will not be providing support for it
I also do not wished to be contacted because I have crippling social anxiety.
